We must appreciate Waqar Ehsin , his voice provided balance and Weight to this song🎶 .  
Have no words to appreciate all the guys who put their sweat , heart and soul to this track.

snippet.textDisplay: I sincerely request the Coke Studios Management to look into setting up a healthy, peaceful and extremely entertaining festival to bring the world together by Coke Studios in so many countries of the world producing creative and entertaining musical creations that attract people of the world regardless of their mother tongue. Pakistan Coke Studio may be the best of them. I was In Canada in 1969 when the Woodstock Music Festival was held in the US. It was the unique and most famous festival for the world wide creative artists. I think it is about time to have a similar and even better and greater COKE STUDIOS MUSIC FESTIVAL.
